      "content": "it's not just about leaving the lab or taking a break. it feels much deeper than that. like even if i quit, i'm still just... stuck in this body, carrying all this failure around. the \"rest\" i'm looking for feels like it has to be more permanent than just a vacation. you get what i mean, right? like the only way to actually be at peace is to just not exist anymore.",
